dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:14:00.000Z","msg":"興趣"},{"pid":"4d228a3d9bc783b11407fc269a9b3f6fae3fad1f","tid":782503,"uid":7638,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:16:28.000Z","msg":"多謝你地, 簡單一句說話令我諗返屋企人對我既好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本仲係覺得佢地對我好令我好內疚好大壓力<br />\n唔知生存為乜,做乜都好冇動力, 愈諗愈負面<br />\n但唔知點解一見到你地簡簡單單講完屋企人三個字又會無啦啦崩堤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你地, 心情好返好多正常返<br />\n多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e94d5ed02a1c83c2618a8732af7babf000a6e9","tid":782503,"uid":175461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:19:24.000Z","msg":"好多年前已經想死<br />\n不過真係實行嗰時會淆哂底<br />\n所以我成日覺得自殺既人真係好犀利，唔其突而其來發顛跳樓嗰種<br />\n<br />\nbtw，唔會再唸自殺，hea住咁過，因為白頭人送黑頭人一定好傷心"},{"pid":"ad42d845ecf33e5f2e67c5cc8303c1883f461df3","tid":782503,"uid":181378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:22:19.000Z","msg":"想發達得到物質同虛榮 想比到屋企人幸福 想朋友以我為榮 但係現實總係一無是處"},{"pid":"310f442a32a8cca61c51874bbf21d5800615208c","tid":782503,"uid":103226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:23:36.000Z","msg":"未睇夠個世界"},{"pid":"266ed3654d9971e454849273af9cc3fa6438fae1","tid":782503,"uid":5065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:40:58.000Z","msg":"前一排有諗過死，但仲有自己理想同埋兩個好重要嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以依家仲生勾勾"},{"pid":"27dd2ea5275596e09bf435c5aa0a594cd93bad79","tid":782503,"uid":199540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:43:56.000Z","msg":"已經經歷過兩次死亡，所以隨時死都得，無遺憾<br />\n不過我想睇到未來，係好係壞都想自己親身去見證<br />\n就係咁繼續生存"},{"pid":"6c22ab680b4439be352d7263e70530fca2c2c9e1","tid":782503,"uid":163248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r4hIeZDH2Qk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/